model.name: Mouse Iron Distribution - Rich iron diet (No Tracer)

body.p: Dynamic model of iron distribution in mice. This model includes only normal iron with the parameters that fit the data from Lopes et al.2010 for mice fed a rich iron diet.
This model does not include the radioiron tracer species. It is appropriate to study the properties in conditions where no tracers are used (for example for steady state analysis).
